                        "description": "Queues a WhatsApp message via the wab (Baileys) service. Returns 202 immediately with a tracking UUID; check delivery status in the dashboard.\n\n**Required fields:** to (number, country code, digits only), message\n\n**Authentication:** X-API-Key header"
                    },
